modules.description: This module extends string manipulation capabilities with operations like splitting strings on delimiters while trimming, extracting substrings before or after specific positions, trimming whitespace or specific characters, converting between strings and lists or arrays, searching for patterns, and replacing substrings. It supports standard string and character types, providing precise control over string decomposition and transformation. Concrete use cases include parsing log lines, processing command-line arguments, sanitizing input data, and implementing custom string formatting logic.
